--- Ingredients

BUILD		How to compilation
COPYING		Copyright
README		This file
RELEASE		Release Note

bin/           ffvc : Executable module

doc/		Documents

doxygen/       Doxygen files
	
example/	example files
	
src/		source files
	Cutlib-x.x.x    cut information library
	F_CORE          f90 subroutines in ffvc
	F_VOF		VOF routines
	FB		base class
	FFV		ffvc class
	IP		intrinsic problems
	PMlib-x.x	performance measurement library
	Polylib-x.x	polygon data management library


--- 　Comments & Known Problems

2012-12-25 流出境界条件としてFAR_FIELDを使うと，計算初期に流出ベクトルが振動する．流れが発達し，一様流速に近づくと振動は小さくなる．
